@startuml virtualFitting
title Sequence Diagram: Virtual Fitting and Size Recommendation

actor Customer

boundary "Frontend\n(React)" as Frontend
control "Backend\n(FastAPI)" as Backend
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
control "Recommendation Engine" as RE
control "Visualization\n(Three.js)" as Viz

Customer -> Frontend : Select garment
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend : Request virtual fitting
activate Backend

Backend -> DB : Retrieve avatar
activate DB
DB --> Backend : Avatar
deactivate DB

Backend -> DB : Retrieve garment
activate DB
DB --> Backend : Garment details
deactivate DB

Backend -> RE : Compare measurements
activate RE

RE --> Backend : Recommended size
deactivate RE

Backend -> Viz : Render virtual fitting
activate Viz

Viz --> Backend : Visualization
deactivate Viz

Backend --> Frontend : Return fitting result
deactivate Backend

Frontend --> Customer : Display avatar and size recommendation
deactivate Frontend

@enduml